Key to the species of 
<taxonomicName id="7A8F3BAC4831C514FE2408196DA8F369" box="[412,673,1592,1618]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Hoplitis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="111" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Formicapis">
<emphasis id="8FFB9C3D4831C514FE2408196EF5F369" bold="true" box="[412,508,1592,1618]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="111">Hoplitis</emphasis>
(
